OL,3,CA step too far? Driver fined over
OL,4,Cladder poking out of car boot
OL,6,FPolice stopped this car after a
OL,7,Fmotorist was spotted driving around
OL,8,Fwith a huge ladder poking out of the
OL,9,Fback of his boot.
OL,11,FOfficers said the bizarre set-up was
OL,12,Fmade even worse by the fact the ladder
OL,13,Fwas not even secured to the vehicle.
OL,15,FLancashire Police said the situation
OL,16,Fpresented a 'clear risk to the public'
OL,17,Fand issued the driver of the Seat Leon
OL,18,Fwith a fine.
