OL,3,CA step too far? Driver fined over
OL,4,Cladder poking out of car boot
OL,6,FA spokesman said: "Our Roads Policing
OL,7,FUnit are committed in preventing
OL,8,Fcollisions and casualties on the road.
OL,10,F"The driver of this vehicle in
OL,11,FBrierfield thought it was acceptable
OL,12,Fto drive with this ladder hanging from
OL,13,Fthe rear of the vehicle with no means
OL,14,Fof making this safe.
OL,16,F"Driving with such a load presents a
OL,17,Frisk of danger to other members of the
OL,18,Fpublic. Fixed Penalty Notice issued
OL,19,Fand ladder removed from the vehicle."
