OL,6,FThe picture was posted on the Nelson,
OL,7,FBrierfield and Barrowford Police
OL,8,FFacebook page - and locals did not
OL,9,Fdisappoint with their quick-witted
OL,10,Fresponses to pictures of the car.
OL,12,FOne said: "Maybe he was trying to get
OL,13,Fhigh?"
OL,15,FAnother commented: "The dizzy heights
OL,16,Fof the standard of driving in and
OL,17,Faround Nelson and Brierfield being
OL,18,Fhigh-lighted yet again."
OL,20,FA third wrote: "That's actually class!
OL,21,FImagine thinking this is okay."
